                        <interp inst="t18420822-name-679" type="given" value="CHARLES"></interp>CHARLES READ</persName>
                  </hi>. I watched the prisoner, and saw him take the lead and put it into his pocket—he was brought back, and I took the lead out of his pocket.</p>
